General.Name: Netbay Public Company Limited
General.Description: Netbay Public Company Limited creates, designs, and develops digital business technology platform and omni channel connectivity gateway solutions for the electronic business transaction exchange in the field of trading. The company provides digital business services, which include e-customs; customs e-payment; e-manifest, a paperless report for imports/ exports system; e-express; electronic transaction reporting gateway for financial institutes; customer due diligence gateways; and software development and cloud computing services. Its software as a service comprise data center, disaster recovery center, operating software system, which supports the electronic transaction reporting gateway, networking systems, and protection of information services. In addition, the company acts as electronic data interchange provider for electronic transaction reporting and audit report services for life insurance, non-life insurance, securities, asset management, and finance companies, as well as financial institutions and banks. Further, it offers electronics bank guarantee data interchange services between banks and Comptroller General's Department. It serves international and domestic trade, and service sectors; manufacturers, exporters, importers, freight forwarders, shipping agents, customs brokers, terminal operators, transportation service providers, and logistics and supply chain communities; ocean line, air, and express couriers; and the Thai Chamber of Commerce and Board of Trade of Thailand. Netbay Public Company Limited was founded in 2004 and is based in Bangkok, Thailand.
